Algorithm to check password

1) Start. Take user input Password.
2) Check whether password contains any space. If yes, print "Invalid" and stop.
3) Check whether password length is between 8 to 16 characters. If not, print "Invalid" and stop.
4) Check whether password contains at least one digit(0-9). If not, print "Invalid" and stop.
5) Check whether password contains at least one lowercase letter(a-z). If not, print "Invalid" and stop.
6) Check whether password contains one uppercase letter(A-Z). If not, print "Invalid" and stop.
7) Check whether password contains at least one special character ( @, #, %, &, !, $, etcâ€¦.). If not, print "Invalid" and stop.
8) Password is Valid. Print "Valid".
9) Stop.
